== Overview ==
The Plasma Shield provides very strong protection but a slow recharge rate. The power to strength ration is also impressive, however the weight of this shield restricts its use to larger bot chassis.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Plasma Shield can be bought in the workshop after acquiring [[Plasma Technology]].
